Mama!

00:13:12.800 --> 00:13:14.160
Dia tidak mengingatku.

00:13:14.560 --> 00:13:16.560
Dia mengingat Aparajita,
tapi dia telah melupakanku!

00:13:16.880 --> 00:13:19.600
Dia telah melupakan kita semua!  Bagaimana mungkin, Nia?
- Mama.

00:13:19.680 --> 00:13:21.240
Ashu, bawakan dia air.

00:13:22.040 --> 00:13:23.160
Tinggalkan aku!  - Asha...

00:13:23.280 --> 00:13:24.600
Asha...
- Bu!

00:13:26.800 --> 00:13:28.520
Bibi, ambilkan air.

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:31.920
Bu, santai saja.

